Title: Fix required comment field for adhoc downtimes
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1618834792
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

If you used adhoc downtimes in previous 2.0 versions, the downtime could not be
send, because the comment field was stated as required after using the button
of the configured adhoc downtime.
